org.cef

Class CefBrowserSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.CefBrowserSettings

  • public class CefBrowserSettings
extends java.lang.Object
    Browser initialization settings. Specify NULL or 0 to get the recommended default values. The consequences of using custom values may not be well tested. Many of these and other settings can also configured using command- line switches.(浏览器初始化设置。指定空或0以获取建议的默认值。使用自定义值的后果可能没有得到很好的测试。其中许多设置和其他设置也可以使用命令行开关进行配置。)

    • Field Detail

      • windowless_frame_rate

        public int windowless_frame_rate
        The maximum rate in frames per second (fps) that CefRenderHandler::OnPaint will be called for a windowless browser. The actual fps may be lower if the browser cannot generate frames at the requested rate. The minimum value is 1 and the maximum value is 60 (default 30). This value can also be changed dynamically via CefBrowser#setWindowlessFrameRate(对于无窗口浏览器，CefRenderHandler：：OnPaint将被调用的最大速率（每秒帧）。如果浏览器无法以请求的速率生成帧，则实际帧秒可能会更低。最小值为1，最大值为60（默认为30）。该值也可以通过CefBrowse #setWindowsFrame速率动态更改)
